---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import FeatureBlock from '../components/FeatureBlock.astro';
---
<Layout title="Insight Hunter Lite: Local First Privacy Focused Finance Software | Offline Runway Calculator">
  <head>
    <meta name="description" content="Insight Hunter Lite is local first privacy focused finance software with offline runway calculator, burn rate tracking, and secure cash flow insights for solo founders." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="local first finance software, privacy focused financial tool, offline runway calculator, secure startup finance app" />
  </head>

  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2.2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Lite is the premier local first privacy focused finance software, offering an offline runway calculator and secure financial tools for solo founders.</p>
    <p style="font-size:2.2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Insight Hunter Lite provides zero-friction, local-first financial intelligence for solo founders and lean operators, delivering immediate clarity without cloud dependencies.</p>
    <p>This edition runs entirely on your machine, ensuring complete data privacy while offering automated P&L snapshots, burn rate and runway calculations, and basic cash flow tracking. Connect banks locally for read-only imports, generating instant insights into financial health. New enhancements include real-time dashboards for key metrics, simple budgeting rules for recurring expenses, and one-click PDF exports of investor-ready reports, including basic balance sheets and unit economics overviews.</p>
    <p>Enjoy introductory scenario planning for personal what-if questions, such as hiring impacts or expense adjustments, powered by lightweight local AI processing. Lite supports CSV imports from accounting tools, laying the foundation for scalable FP&A as your needs grow. All data remains on-device, with no external syncing required.</p>
    <img src="/images/lite-mockup.png" alt="Lite real-time dashboard and reports" class="feature-image">
    <p>For seamless upgrades to advanced forecasting and integrations, explore Standard or Full editions. Company updates on Lite enhancements are available in the updates section.</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta" style="display:inline-block; margin:60px auto;">Download Lite Free</a>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <FeatureBlock title="Local AI Insights" text="Natural language queries provide instant answers on runway, burn rate, or expense trends directly from your local data." image="/images/ai-query-mockup.png" alt="Local AI query example" />
    <FeatureBlock title="Automated Basic Reports" text="Generate P&L statements, cash flow overviews, and simple forecasts offline for quick investor sharing." image="/images/mobile-mockup.png" alt="Offline report exports" reverse />
  </section>
</Layout>
---
